\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And you're a widow and when were you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 '19. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And your date of birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Was the second of June 1900.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And your birthplace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Rosscommon. In Ireland. Yes. Southern Ireland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Can you tell me how many years you lived in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Where I was born? I must have lived in eight years because I was born in that house and - I came from - come from there to here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 When you were eight you came over from Rosscommon to live with your paternal grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 At Dresden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And you stayed in that one house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 About - thirty-two - thirty-five years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Can you tell me why you came over to England, you came over by yourself you told me? Your parents stayed in Ireland?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes. My dad brought me over to me grandmother because - well - I think they didn't want me. I don't think me mother wanted me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And your grandmother here was willing to look after you and give you a home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 You had no brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 No, I had no brothers and sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 How old was your father when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 I should say about forty, I don't - I don't know really how old he was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 He was seventy-eight when he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes, when he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And when was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Well say '51, I don't know whether it was '51 or '52 when he died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Your father was Irish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And he came from Rosscommon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Rosscommon, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Was well - horse - he sold horses and that you know, bred horses and had a farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And as far as you know this was inherited from his own father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh yes, it came from his own father. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 You don't know how old your mother was when you were born but you think she was about Eighty when she died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 When she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And that was around 1950?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes. About 1950 - something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And your mother too was Irish and originated from Rosscommon as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And your mother was a kind of village nurse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 That's right. That's as far as I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 She would go round the villages attending people who were being confined?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And who were sick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And as far as you know that was the only job she had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 She did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 
Your mother did work after she had you and for the first eight years you were living with your parents and also with grandparents and your father's sisters on the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And the whole family were helping to bring you up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Can you describe the house that you lived in in Dresden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Well, it was a - a back to back house if you understand what I mean to say, it came at the back, each gate did and ther
e was like a long passage affair that we used to play in but - it was a four bedroomed house but - oh at that back of course we had to have, granddad used to go to and I had a back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 What rooms would they be downstairs then, two rooms downstairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 
Wait a minute, there was one, two - there was three rooms downstairs and a scullery, but the scullery came off if you understand what I mean to say. It wasn't like this, it wasn't adjoined, there was a little kitchen and then a little passage and then the
 scullery came off. Then of course the toilet and everything was outside. And - but there was nothing - nothing really convenient, you know what I mean to say, that - there was nothing - if anyone was taken ill or anything like that, well, if they wanted 
- a bedpan or anything like that they had to use a bucket or something like that, there was nothing really - you know what I mean to say, there was no - there's no - no sanitation at all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 What were the rooms downstairs, you had a sort of scullery, and you had a parlour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 
Yes, grandma used to use that for parties you know, if we had a birthday or anything like that and the kitchen she used to use for the - you know, for us to have our food and the rest of it and - the scullery she used to do the wa
shing in. And this little out place she used to use for either cooking or anything like that you know. She'd got a little table in and used to do her cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Who else besides your grandparents and you lived in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Another aunt. Another -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Your mother's sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes. She was only a young }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621 g}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 
l like me, we were brought up together. You see, my grandma had my aunt Edie rather late in life. I think that's reason why they took to me so much because I was nearly the same age as Edie, only about twelve month older than I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 So there were no lodgers or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh no. No, she had no lodgers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Did your grandma pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 No. She couldn't, she couldn't afford - we had to help gran when we got old enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 The washing was done in the back kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Kitchen. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 It wouldn't be sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Did your gran mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes, she used to make all our clothes. Oh yes. She used to cut up old - well 
she used to go and - well to tell you the truth she used to buy them off the rag carts and then cut them up and make frocks and that for us, but we were always well dressed. I think she was a trained nurse by trade, before she got married, but she did no 
work. That's what I mean to say, she did no outside work.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Were your parents supporting you at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh yes, me parents were supporting me. Yes, they were sending money over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 But still things were hard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh it were hard. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Can you remember having new clothes?
