Well - I had new clothes of course when I got married but - gran always used to buy materials and have them - and make it for the Corpus Christi and that for both of us, we always had a new frock for the Corpus Ch
risti, white like you know with the veil. If I'm not mistaken it was an old wedding veil that she cut up for the two girls. But those are the only new clothes I remember having. And of course grandad used to do our shoes, he used to get - buy shoes you kn
ow, for us, and when they wanted mending he mended.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 But you would usually have new shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 
yes, we'd have new shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And your granddad would be able to cobble them himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes. They'd last us about eight or nine month anyhow, as schoolchildren. Of course the best shoes had got to last - yes.
