randdad had got a small pony and trap and - he used to - him and grandma used to go out and then they used to bring us stuff back. They never used to let us choose our own you know. And we always had good food really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Did your granddad help your gran with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 No, only just }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
