\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh he did the decorating, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And repairs to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh no. The landlord used to do all the repairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Would he help with you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Well he used to take us out on a Sunday morning, a good walk, while grandma - cooked our dinners and that. What did he do - tak
e us out - perhaps in the summer nights he'd take us in the park, the Longton Park. Oh yes, he'd help with us - like as far as going out was concerned and then he - he used to play with us, games such at top and whip and bowlers and like that, he'd play w
ith us and - until we got too old you know. You know how we were - well, of course you don't know how we were in them days, we used to get right misses you know, of course we got to go -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 But as far as dressing you or undressing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Bathing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 But he would take you out, would this be without your gran?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Did he read to you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes, he'd read a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 bedtime story to us if - if we asked him. If we didn't ask him he didn't bother. But if we asked him he'd read a bedtime story to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Did your gran ever go out and leave your granddad to look after the two girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 No, she - if she went out she always used to - leave us with -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home in order to help your gran and granddad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 
Well yes, we used to take our turns in washing the dishes and that up for her and - we used to - take our turns in going and fetching little things from the shops you know and the rest of it. And then we used to go an
d fetch the papers each - in our turn like, one one Sunday and the other another Sunday. Took our turns like in errands like that and washing dishes and - a time or two - me aunt's don}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621 e}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621  the baking for her, but - I was never - never taught to bake, you know
. To tell you the truth, when I got married I didn't know how to - she was a bit on the funny side, she wouldn't have showed you - to do with food nor nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 So you were expected to do certain things in the house but they weren't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621 m}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 ore than you would expect any normal girl to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 How long did you carry on doing these jobs, did you do them after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes, I did it after I left school but - I left grandma when I was fifteen and went with a friend and - got i
n with this fellow and got married and - and of course we got a house of our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 You were the youngest child in the family when you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 And there was only you and your auntie Edie, who were more or less the same age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time while you were at school?
