\insrsid15293131\charrsid7613621 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 hing, and - other times she let us go on our own you know. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Did you share the bedroom or the bed with anyone?
