\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Well he'd have food same as we 
