 it wasn't - wasn't - daddy. No, granddad used to drill it in me that he wasn't me daddy, but me grandma never used to do, she used to think I - I ought to call her mummy and - I tre}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11608852\charrsid7613621 a}{
