\insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 s.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Are both these schools in Longton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 No. They were at Stoke. Stoke. Yes. St Peters church at Stoke is - St Dominic}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11608852\charrsid7613621 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 s - St Dominic}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11608852\charrsid7613621 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 
s is by there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 These were both Catholic schools?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh yes, Catholic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid221165 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Were these mixed schools?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14048569 AN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2973543\charrsid7613621 Oh mixed. Yes.
